<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 27 at 8:35PM EST  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...Dense Fog Tonight...
Plan on patches of dense for tonight around Lynchburg, east
toward Farmville and southeast to Charlotte Court House.
Visibility will be less than one half mile to near zero in spots.
These conditions will change little for the rest of the evening.
Use caution when traveling in the Virginia foothills and piedmont
tonight. Slow down, use low-beam headlights, and allow plenty of
time to reach your destination.</description>
